        <DIV class="wiki-content">
          <P>In the <A href="validating-input.html" title="Validating Input">Validating Input</A> lesson, we used the validation framework to verify data submitted from a form. In the <EM>Localizing Output</EM> lesson, we move the validation messages to a message resource bundle. </P>

<P>When creating web applications, we often find ourselves using the same messages or field labels on multiple pages. We may also want to localize the messages if the application is going to be used by people of different languages. </P>

<H2><A name="LocalizingOutput-LocalizingValidationMessagesandFields"></A>Localizing Validation Messages and Fields</H2>

<P>Let's add a message resource bundle and move into it the validation messages and field labels.</P>

<H3><A